## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical implementation of PIM for cross-tenant vendor access scenarios; validates understanding of governance, auditability, and emergency access controls in real-world incident response environments.

## Key Concepts
- Privileged Identity Management (PIM)
- Eligible vs Active assignments
- Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)
- Approval workflows
- Just-in-time activation
- Conditional Access integration
- Audit logging and monitoring
- Automatic revocation mechanisms
- Cross-tenant access patterns
- Time-bound access controls
- Compliance reporting

## Code Example
```javascript
// PIM activation request configuration
const pimRequest = {
  roleId: 'incident-admin-role',
  justification: 'Critical incident response - vendor access required',
  duration: 'PT4H', // 4 hours maximum
